data.description: You do not  want to miss out on this property. This like-new property will make moving a breeze. It comes already equipped with top notch finishes. The cool color scheme makes personalizing this home  easy. The main living space has tile flooring throughout. Entertaining will be easy with the open floor plan and the abundance of counter space with the island. The kitchen in outfitted with stainless steel appliances. The indoor laundry room is large enough for endless options.  The master suite is very spacious and includes a large walk in closet, double vanity and tile flooring. The exterior has a lot to offer as well. This large corner lot offers a great space to relax on the front porch or you can opt to sit in the large fenced in backyard. This property has everything you need.
